#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">kwallet-query</emphasis> <emphasis>OPTIONS</"
"emphasis> <emphasis>wallet</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">kwallet-query</emphasis> <emphasis>MOŽNOSTI</"
"emphasis> <emphasis>denarnica</emphasis>"

#. Tag: title
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "DESCRIPTION"
msgstr "OPIS"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>kwallet-query</command> comes in handy when shell scripts need to "
"read or update the &kde; Wallet. It works by manipulating the entries "
"displayed in the <emphasis role=\"strong\">&kde; Wallet Manager</emphasis> "
"utility. It&#8217;s only parameter is the <emphasis>wallet</emphasis>name "
"the tool should read or update. The operation mode is specified by the "
"options."
msgstr ""
"<command>kwallet-query</command> je uporaben, ko morajo skripte lupine "
"prebrati ali posodobiti &kde; Denarnico. Deluje s pomočjo manipulacije "
"vnosov, prikazanih v pripomočku <emphasis role=\"strong\">&kde;-jevega "
"Upravljalnika denarnice</emphasis>. Njegov&#8217; edini parameter je ime "
"<emphasis>denarnice</emphasis>, ki naj jo orodje prebere ali posodobi. Način "
"delovanja je določen z možnostmi."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "OPTIONS"
msgstr "MOŽNOSTI"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "-h,--help"
msgstr "-h,--help"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display a short help message."
msgstr "Prikaži kratko sporočilo o pomoči."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid "-l,--list-entries"
msgstr "-l,--list-entries"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"List password entries. These are the folder names displayed in the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">&kde; Wallet Manager</emphasis> utility. If the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">-f</emphasis> option is given, this will only display the "
"subfolders of the specified folder."
msgstr ""
"Prikaži seznam vnosov. To so imena map, ki so prikazana na pripomočku "
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">&kde;-jev Upravljalnik denarnice</emphasis>. Če je "
"navedena možnost <emphasis role=\"strong\">-f</emphasis>, bodo prikazane le "
"podmape navedene datoteke."

#. Tag: term
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">-r,--read-password</emphasis> <emphasis>Entry</"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">-r,--read-password</emphasis> <emphasis>Vnos</"
"emphasis>"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Read the contents of the given <emphasis>Entry</emphasis> from the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Folder</emphasis>section of the <emphasis>wallet</emphasis> "
"and output it on the standard output. Maps are exported as &JSON; object."
msgstr ""
"Preberi vsebino podanega <emphasis>Vnosa</emphasis> iz razdelka <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Mapa</emphasis>, ki je del <emphasis>denarnice</emphasis>, "
"in jo izpiši na standardni vhod. Preslikave so izvožene v obliki &JSON; "
"objektov."

#. Tag: term
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">-w,--write-password</emphasis> <emphasis>Entry</"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">-w,--write-password</emphasis> <emphasis>Vnos</"
"emphasis>"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Write secrets to the given <emphasis>Entry</emphasis> under the <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Folder</emphasis> section of the given <emphasis>wallet</"
"emphasis>. The secrets are read from the standard input. Maps take in input "
"a well-formed &JSON; object. <emphasis role=\"strong\">IMPORTANT</emphasis> "
"previous wallet entry value will be overwritten by this option, so be "
"careful when using it!"
msgstr ""
"Napiši skrivnosti na podan <emphasis>Vhod</emphasis> pod razdelkom <emphasis "
"role=\"strong\">Mapa</emphasis> podane <emphasis>denarnice</emphasis>. "
"Skrivnosti so brane iz standardnega vhoda. Preslikave vzamejo vnos v obliki "
"&JSON; objekta. <emphasis role=\"strong\">POMEMBNO</emphasis> prejšnje "
"vrednosti vnosov v denarnico bodo prepisani s to možnostjo, zato bodite "
"pazljivi, ko jo uporabljate!"

#. Tag: term
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">-f,--folder</emphasis> <emphasis>Folder</emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"<emphasis role=\"strong\">-f,--folder</emphasis> <emphasis>Mapa</emphasis>"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:87
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the <emphasis>wallet</emphasis> folder to <emphasis>Folder</emphasis> "
"value. By default <emphasis role=\"strong\">Passwords</emphasis> is used."
msgstr ""
"Nastavi mapo <emphasis>denarnice</emphasis> na vrednost <emphasis>Mapa</"
"emphasis>. Privzeto je uporabljeno <emphasis role=\"strong\">Geslo</"
"emphasis>."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid "-v,--verbose"
msgstr "-v,--verbose"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:95
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Output more information when performing the operation, to help debugging."
msgstr ""
"Izpiši več informacij med izvajanjem opravila, za pomoč pri razhroščevanju."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "EXIT STATUS"
msgstr "IZHODNO STANJE"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:106
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>0</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>0</emphasis>"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid "Success."
msgstr "Uspešno."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>1</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>1</emphasis>"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "The wallet <emphasis>wallet</emphasis> was not found."
msgstr "Denarnica <emphasis>denarnica</emphasis> ni bila najdena."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>2</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>2</emphasis>"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The wallet <emphasis>wallet</emphasis> could not be opened. For example, "
"that would be an indication of a bad password entry or some other problem "
"with the &kde; Wallet system."
msgstr ""
"Denarnice <emphasis>denarnica</emphasis> ni bilo mogoče odpreti. To bi lahko "
"bila posledica npr. napačnega vnosa gesla ali katerega drugega problema s "
"&kde;-jevim sistemom Denarnic."

#. Tag: emphasis
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>3</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>3</emphasis>"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"strong\">Folder</emphasis> section was not found inside "
"the wallet <emphasis>wallet</emphasis>. Perhaps the wallet file is corrupt?"
msgstr ""
"Razdelka <emphasis role=\"strong\">Mapa</emphasis> ni bilo mogoče najti v "
"denarnici <emphasis>denarnica</emphasis>. Mogoče je datoteka z denarnico "
"poškodovana?"

#. Tag: emphasis
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "<emphasis>4</emphasis>"
msgstr "<emphasis>4</emphasis>"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:145
#, no-c-format
msgid "The read or write operation has failed for some reason."
msgstr "Operacija branje ali pisanje iz nekega razloga ni uspela."

#. Tag: title
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:152
#, no-c-format
msgid "BUGS"
msgstr "HROŠČI"

#. Tag: simpara
#: man-kwallet-query.1.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Please report all bugs on the &kde; bug reporting website: bugs.kde.org. Be "
"sure to select <quote>kwallet-query</quote> when submitting your bug-report."
msgstr ""
"Prosimo, prijavite vse hrošče na &kde;-jevi strani za prijavljanje hroščev: "
"bugs.kde.org. Bodite pozorni, da pri oddaji vašega poročila izberete "
"<quote>kwallet-query</quote>."

